        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
            <title>Service Procedure</title>
            <specpara>
                <warning>
                    <para>To prevent possible property damage, personal injury or death, park the vehicle on a flat
                        level surface, put the transmission in neutral, set the parking brake, chock the wheels, and
                        turn the engine off.
                    </para>
                </warning>
            </specpara>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove the clutch bellhousing inspection cover.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove the clutch release bearing grease zerk fitting.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install the "U" shaped clip from Kit Number 8000830R91 between the clutch release yoke
                    and the release bearing housing with the "U" clip tab (Figure 1, Item 3) oriented rearward toward
                    the transmission.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f039051" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../afcfigures/g039051.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="312px"/>
                <caption>Figure 1. Kit Components</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. THREADED ADAPTER</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. BELLEVILLE WASHER</callout1>
                    <callout1>3. "U" CLIP TAB</callout1>
                    <callout1>4. "U" CLIP</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="f039052" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../afcfigures/g039052.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="272px"/>
                <caption>Figure 2. Kit Installed as Viewed from the Engine Side</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. "U" CLIP</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. ROLLER YOKE</callout1>
                    <callout1>3. RELEASE BEARING HOUSING</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install the threaded adapter and belleville washer through the "U" shaped clip into the
                    zerk fitting hole in the release bearing housing (Figure 2). Tighten to 20 to 25 Lbf-ft (27 to 34
                    Nm).
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install the grease zerk fitting into the threaded adapter.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Reinstall the inspection cover to the clutch bellhousing.</para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
